To build llvm:
1- mkdir LLVM/build
2- cd LLVM/build
3- cmake ../llvm
4- make


Below are the main files that include the implementation of the
detection and the elimination passes.
Main Files:
----------
LLVM/llvm/lib/Analysis/SIMDDeadlockAnalysisNvidia.cpp
LLVM/llvm/lib/Transforms/Scalar/SIMDDeadlockEliminationNvidia.cpp

Test cases will be submitted soon.